# `src/wifi_creds.rs` used to be gitignored back when it held real SSID/PASS
# values. As of v0.8.0 the file is empty (NVS is the source of truth) so we
# commit it. If you want to skip the captive-portal step on a brand-new
# board, edit it locally with your creds, build, flash — those values get
# migrated into NVS on first boot and the file is unused after that.
